=== EVENT_ANCIENT_ARTIFACT ===
# id: 20
# title: Ancient Artifact
# chinese_title: 古代遗物
# category: Discovery
# mode: starmap

Buried within an asteroid, you discover an artifact covered in quantum glyphs. It hums with an energy your instruments cannot classify.

* [Study the quantum glyphs]
  ~ gain_radical("古")
  研究 (yánjiū) — study
* [Sell the artifact at the next port]
  ~ gain_credits(25)
  出售 (chūshòu) — sell
* [Activate the artifact]
  ~ gain_fuel(10)
  激活 (jīhuó) — activate
